| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1549 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 12bca5d7-ef84-5ee3-a2b8-6e081d3c2087"
